Remove the variable and it should work, Just add: 
`<remove type="obs" name="obs" />`
to the one already you have. 

@lesserwhirls I think this a bug. The `joinExisting` aggregation is on _existing_ dimension and it should no required _existing_ variable. Of course if the variable exists, the `coordValues` attribute and `timeChangeUnits` features related to the variable values should be considered.

